This has one correct solution in finite environments.

So Q-Learning converges to optimal values.

8️⃣ Important Things to Remember

Q-Learning is model-free.

It learns from experience.

It balances exploration and exploitation.

It learns values, not paths.

Optimal path is formed by choosing highest Q action in every state.

🔑 One-Line Memory

Q-Learning learns the long-term value of each action in each state and chooses the action with the highest value.